nodes.text: Lillindri Nanimei Filda Vandelhelm XXXII, best known as Lilli, was one of the last two heirs of the Vandel and Helm lines around the time of the Battle of Endor. Lilli and her younger brother Endrodanar Tiopuld Shaamador Vandelhelm XXIV were the Venerated Ones of Vandelhelm during the Galactic Civil War.
